      • init

        public void init​(java.lang.String difficulty,
                 java.lang.String mapFileName,
                 java.lang.String scoreFileName,
                 java.lang.String mapName,
                 javafx.scene.paint.Color color)
        Call this method to pass data to this controller.
        Parameters:
        difficulty - Difficulty of the pacman game, "easy", "medium" or "hard".
        mapFileName - File name of the map to load (e.g. "./recources/maps/cookieComplex.txt")
        scoreFileName - File name of the leaderboard for the provided map
        mapName - Name of the map (not a file name just a name to display to user)
        color - Color which the maze should have when the pacman game starts
